---
title: Southeast Asian Double Chicken & Roasted Pumpkin with Soy-Garlic Greens & Coconut Sauce
description: This simple yet stunning meal is sure to amaze and delight. It’s the perfect combination of tender chicken with an aromatic ginger and coconut sauce and sweet roasted pumpkin.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

